// Section
// Content section with a configurable heading level (h1–h6) and optional collapse toggle.

FUNCTION getHeadingTag(level) -> string
  Returns the appropriate HTML heading tag ("h1"–"h6") for the given level prop.

---

FUNCTION getHeadingSizeClasses(level) -> string
  Returns Tailwind font-size classes appropriate for the heading level.

---

FUNCTION Section(props) -> ReactNode                                      EXPORT
  Renders a section element with a heading at the configured level.
  IF collapsible is true, renders a toggle button next to the heading; clicking it shows or hides the content.
  Content is always visible when collapsible is false.
